      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency assessment between validation and COU input parameters is not required at MRL 2. The COU and validation share the same geometry, fluid properties, and operating envelope, so no significant parameter mismatch exists."
