    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40-2018 framework. Validation results demonstrate CFD-predicted NIH within 13.1% of bench measurements across the full COU operating envelope, satisfying the 15% acceptance criterion. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 is confirmed at all 5 operating points. The overall credibility body of evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
